---
<BaseLayout
  title="Services et tarifs - Valade et associés"
  description="Services d'huissiers pour entreprises et particuliers: signification, exécution de jugement, constats, services connexes et tarification."
>
  <section class="section page-hero" style={`--page-hero-image: url('${assets.servicesHero}')`}>
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <p class="eyebrow">Services et tarifs</p>
      <h1>Des services d'huissiers pour tous</h1>
      <p class="lead">Chez Valade et associés, huissiers de justice, nous vous proposons une gamme complète de services pour tous les types de besoins.</p>
      <div class="service-jumps" aria-label="Accès rapide aux domaines de services">
        <a class="jump-button blue" href="#services-entreprises">Entreprise</a>
        <a class="jump-button gold" href="#services-particuliers">Particulier</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="services-entreprises" class="section service-domain">
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="eyebrow">Services aux entreprises</p>
      <div class="services-board">
        {businessServices.map((service) => (
          <article class="service-card">
            <h2>{service.title}</h2>
            <p>{service.text}</p>
            {service.groupTitle && <h3>{service.groupTitle}</h3>}
            <ul class="service-list">
              {service.items.map((item) => <li>{item}</li>)}
            </ul>
          </article>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="services-particuliers" class="section alt service-domain personal-domain">
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="eyebrow">Services aux particuliers</p>
      <div class="services-board">
        {personalServices.map((service) => (
          <article class="service-card">
            <h2>{service.title}</h2>
            {service.sections.map((section) => (
              <div class="service-block">
                {section.heading && <h3>{section.heading}</h3>}
                {section.paragraphs?.map((paragraph) => <p>{paragraph}</p>)}
                {section.items && (
                  <ul class="service-list">
                    {section.items.map((item) => <li>{item}</li>)}
                  </ul>
                )}
              </div>
            ))}
          </article>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section tariff-section">
    <div class="wrap split">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Mode de tarification</p>
        <h2>Des honoraires encadrés</h2>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p>Les services professionnels rendus par les huissiers de justice sont tarifés par le Tarif d’honoraires des huissiers de justice. Ainsi, les huissiers de justice ont le devoir professionnel de respecter et d’appliquer ce règlement. D’autre part, pour les services connexes rendus à leurs clients, les huissiers peuvent convenir d’une tarification extrajudiciaire en vertu du Tarif d’honoraires professionnels (T.H.P.). Vous trouverez également ci-dessus un document présentant quelques exemples concrets de tarification de mandats d’huissiers qui nous sont fréquemment confiés.</p>
        <div class="tariff-downloads">
          {tariffs.map((tariff) => (
            <a class="tariff-card" href={tariff.href} download>
              <span class="tariff-card-main">
                <img src={assets.pdfIcon} alt="" loading="lazy" />
                <span>{tariff.title}</span>
              </span>
              <span class="tariff-card-action">Télécharger</span>
            </a>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .service-jumps {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 34px;
  }

  .jump-button {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-width: 140px;
    min-height: 50px;
    padding: 12px 20px;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .jump-button.blue {
    background: var(--blue);
  }

  .jump-button.gold {
    background: #e0b529;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .service-domain {
    scroll-margin-top: 110px;
  }

  .service-domain .eyebrow {
    color: var(--blue);
  }

  .personal-domain .service-card h2 {
    color: #dba917;
    border-color: #dba917;
  }

  .services-board {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 18px;
  }

  .service-card {
    min-width: 0;
    padding: clamp(22px, 3vw, 30px);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    background: #fff;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
  }

  .service-card h2 {
    width: 100%;
    margin: 0 0 22px;
    padding: 0 0 14px;
    border-top: 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--blue);
    color: var(--blue);
    font-size: clamp(24px, 3vw, 34px);
    text-align: left;
  }

  .service-card h3 {
    margin: 20px 0 10px;
    color: var(--blue);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.25;
  }

  .personal-domain .service-card h3 {
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .service-card p {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .service-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .service-list li {
    position: relative;
    margin: 9px 0;
    padding-left: 20px;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.45;
  }

  .service-list li::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: .68em;
    width: 7px;
    height: 7px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--blue);
  }

  .personal-domain .service-list li::before {
    background: #dba917;
  }

  .service-block + .service-block {
    margin-top: 18px;
    padding-top: 14px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .tariff-downloads {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 18px;
    margin-top: 30px;
  }

  .tariff-section {
    background: var(--grid-surface);
    background-size: var(--grid-size);
  }

  .tariff-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 20px;
    min-height: 118px;
    padding: 18px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #385695 0%, #2f4d89 100%);
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 26px rgba(21, 38, 80, .14);
    transition: transform .18s ease, box-shadow .18s ease;
  }

  .tariff-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 16px 32px rgba(21, 38, 80, .2);
  }

  .tariff-card:nth-child(2) {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f2c510 0%, #e2b708 100%);
  }

  .tariff-card-main {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 18px;
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
    padding: 0;
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.28;
  }

  .tariff-card-main img {
    width: 74px;
    height: 74px;
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    object-fit: contain;
    padding: 14px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    background: rgba(18, 34, 76, .32);
  }

  .tariff-card-action {
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    min-width: 142px;
    min-height: 48px;
    padding: 12px 18px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: #223f79;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .tariff-card:nth-child(2) .tariff-card-main img {
    background: rgba(132, 102, 0, .22);
  }

  .tariff-card:nth-child(2) .tariff-card-action {
    background: #cfa800;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    .services-board {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 680px) {
    .services-board {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .jump-button {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 260px;
    }

    .tariff-downloads {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
    }

    .tariff-card {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .tariff-card-action {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
